OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,FPeople living on a road in
OL,7,FSouthampton, close to where Henry
OL,8,FNowak died, have told ITV Meridian
OL,9,Flast night's violent disorder was
OL,10,F'terrifying'.
OL,12,FHundreds of people marched to
OL,13,FPortswood Police station on Tuesday
OL,14,Fevening, before clashing with police
OL,15,Fon Belmont road.
OL,17,FBottles were thrown, makeshift weapons
OL,18,Fused, and damage was caused to the
OL,19,Fhomes and vehicles of innocent
OL,20,Fresidents, Hampshire Police said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
