CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,FThis morning, the community came
OL,7,Ftogether to begin the clear-up, after
OL,8,Fsome areas were left looking like a
OL,9,F'war zone'.
OL,11,FLocal resident, Sophie Martin, told
OL,12,FITV Meridian her cars were 'smashed
OL,13,Fup' and the protests were horrible.
OL,15,F"It was terrifying", she said. "Our
OL,16,Fcars have been smashed up. The boys
OL,17,Fwere asleep upstairs... it was
OL,18,Fhorrible. Like a war zone.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@SO]wD@`OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,F"It lasted for four hours... half
OL,7,Fseven to half eleven. Then we had to
OL,8,Fcome out and tape the cars up as it
OL,9,Fwas raining.
OL,11,F"It's horrible still to be honest,
OL,12,Fstill got that funny feeling in my
OL,13,Ftummy."
OL,15,FSophie Martin's cars were smashed by
OL,16,Fprotesters.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
