PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,FFurther down the road Dennis Darley
OL,7,Fsaid he was watching from his house as
OL,8,Fgroups walked down the road throwing
OL,9,Fbins and bottles, in what he has
OL,10,Fcompared to a war zone.
OL,12,F"We saw it last night, all the trouble
OL,13,Fand everything", he told ITV Meridian.
OL,14,F"The groups coming up the road
OL,15,Fthrowing bins and bottles and
OL,16,Fsticks... it was like a war zone.
OL,18,F"It was really bad. But, this murder
OL,19,Facross the road. It's got everyone's
OL,20,Fback up".
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@OO]vD@AOUzD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
