PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,FDennis Darley described last night's
OL,7,Fprotests as a war zone.
OL,9,FSouthampton City Council confirmed it
OL,10,Fwas helping with the clean-up today,
OL,11,Fand urged for unity following the
OL,12,Fdisorder overnight.
OL,14,FIn a joint statement from the Leader
OL,15,Fof the Council, Councillor Sarah
OL,16,FBogle, and Councillor Toqeer Kataria,
OL,17,FCabinet Member for Communities, Safety
OL,18,Fand Leisure, they said: "Last night's
OL,19,Fevents in our city were deeply
OL,20,Fconcerning, and I know many residents
OL,21,Fwill be feeling unsettled this morning.
OL,26,@zD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain first and
OL,7,Fforemost with the family and friends
OL,8,Fof Henry Nowak. His death was an
OL,9,Fappalling and unforgivable crime and
OL,10,Fhas had a profound impact across our
OL,11,Fcity.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,F"Southampton is a city that has always
OL,7,Ftaken pride in the strength of our
OL,8,Fcommunities to come together in
OL,9,Fdifficult times. There is no excuse
OL,10,Ffor the kind of violence and disorder
OL,11,Fwe saw last night. While there are
OL,12,Funderstandably strong views about the
OL,13,Fpolice's handling of Henry Nowak's
OL,14,Fmurder, it is important that we allow
OL,15,Fthe IOPC to conduct a thorough,
OL,16,Ftransparent, and independent
OL,17,Finvestigation so that the facts are
OL,18,Fclearly established.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,F"This is a moment for responsible
OL,7,Fleadership at every level. Those
OL,8,Fcommenting from outside our city
OL,9,Fshould take care not to use language
OL,10,Fthat could inflame tensions. Our
OL,11,Fpriority must be to respect Henry
OL,12,FNowak's memory and support our
OL,13,Fcommunities to come together, not add
OL,14,Fto division.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,F"Council crews are out this morning to
OL,7,Fclear the damage caused by last
OL,8,Fnight's disorder and there will be an
OL,9,Fincreased community safety and
OL,10,Freassurance presence in the affected
OL,11,Fareas. We will continue to work with
OL,12,Four communities and partners to keep
OL,13,FSouthampton a safe, inclusive, and
OL,14,Fwelcoming city for all.
OL,16,F"At times like this, it is more
OL,17,Fimportant than ever that we stand
OL,18,Ftogether and focus on what unites us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
