PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780503064
OL,3,CViolent disorder on street where Henry
OL,4,CNowak died 'terrifying' neighbours say,
OL,6,FTensions have been rising since police
OL,7,Fbodycam footage was released on Monday
OL,8,Fnight, showing an officer handcuffing
OL,9,FMr Nowak as he lay dying from stab
OL,10,Fwounds.
OL,12,FThe footage was made public after
OL,13,FVickrum Digwa, 23, was jailed for life
OL,14,Ffor murdering the 18-year-old
OL,15,FUniversity of Southampton student with
OL,16,Fa Sikh ceremonial knife.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
